name.k: 超高層ビル ~ あそんでまなぼう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 了解如何建造和管理摩天大楼。
Learn to build and manage a towering skyscraper.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: What are those towers that touch the sky? Tinybop’s awesome sandbox teaches kids the fun way—by letting them build, watch, and play. As they add floors and test the effects of plumbing problems and earthquakes, they're actually learning basic design and engineering principles. Amazing details abound—from all the busy little inhabitants to the full-blown skyline you can make.
